OL,3,CAfter 20 days of silence - CEO of
OL,4,CSouth East Water says 'I won't resign'
OL,6,FAfter refusing to answer questions in
OL,7,Fpublic for 20 days since the water
OL,8,Foutage in Tunbridge Wells, the chief
OL,9,Fexecutive of South East Water has said
OL,10,Fhe won't resign.
OL,12,FIn his first interview since the
OL,13,Foutage in November left tens of
OL,14,Fthousands of people without clean
OL,15,Fwater, David Hinton, CEO of South East
OL,16,FWater, said he always intended to
OL,17,Fspeak in public and was 'in the engine
OL,18,Froom' while the crisis unfolded.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G1/15
