OL,3,CAfter 20 days of silence - CEO of
OL,4,CSouth East Water says 'I won't resign'
OL,6,FHe insisted that he won't step down
OL,7,Fand has plans to improve the company's
OL,8,Finfrastructure.
OL,10,F"I always intended to do interviews at
OL,11,Fthis point to fully explain the bigger
OL,12,Fpicture," he told ITV Meridian.
OL,14,F"I felt like I was needed in the
OL,15,Fengine room to try and solve this
OL,16,Fissue, make those big procurement
OL,17,Fdecisions for all the different
OL,18,Fchemicals - I was in the thick of
OL,19,Fthose and in the incident.
OL,21,F"I always intended to come out now."
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G2/15
