OL,3,CAfter 20 days of silence - CEO of
OL,4,CSouth East Water says 'I won't resign'
OL,6,FEarlier this year, Hinton's base
OL,7,Fsalary was increased by more than 30%
OL,8,Fto #400,000.
OL,10,FAsked whether he would resign, he
OL,11,Freplied: "I feel like I've got the
OL,12,Fteam behind me and we've got the plan
OL,13,Fto be able to deliver (infrastructure
OL,14,Fimprovements) and actually ensure this
OL,15,Fdoesn't happen going forward."
OL,17,FGiving the first detailed explanation
OL,18,Ffor the cause of the outage, Hinton
OL,19,Fsuggested climate change was a factor.
