OL,3,CAfter 20 days of silence - CEO of
OL,4,CSouth East Water says 'I won't resign'
OL,6,FHe said that a record-breaking summer
OL,7,Fand lack of rainfall changed the make-
OL,8,Fup of the spring water which feeds the
OL,9,Freservoir for Tunbridge Wells.
OL,11,FThis meant the usual treatment
OL,12,Fchemicals didn't work, which the
OL,13,Fcompany initially thought was due to a
OL,14,Fnew batch of coagulants.
OL,16,F"What we saw coming to the last
OL,17,Fweekend of November is that process
OL,18,Fstopped functioning as it had done for
OL,19,Fyears," he said. "We had to
OL,20,Finvestigate why that was."
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G4/15
