OL,3,CAfter 20 days of silence - CEO of
OL,4,CSouth East Water says 'I won't resign'
OL,6,FHinton said the company tested five
OL,7,Fvariations of the chemicals before it
OL,8,Ffound one which worked, which is why
OL,9,Fit took so long to resolve.
OL,11,F"That impacted both our comms -
OL,12,Fbecause we thought we were going to
OL,13,Fresolve it with the first change of
OL,14,Fchemicals - but it didn't ultimately
OL,15,Fresolve it until we managed to procure
OL,16,Fa completely alternative type of
OL,17,Fcoagulant."
