OL,3,CAfter 20 days of silence - CEO of
OL,4,CSouth East Water says 'I won't resign'
OL,6,FMore than 24,000 homes in Tunbridge
OL,7,FWells were left without clean drinking
OL,8,Fwater when the treatment plant in
OL,9,Fstopped working - leaving families,
OL,10,Fschools, and GP surgeries without
OL,11,Frunning water and costing business
OL,12,Fthousands of pounds.
OL,14,FAddressing questions of lost
OL,15,Fcommercial revenue and disruption to
OL,16,Fhouseholds, Hinton apologised.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G6/15
