OL,3,CAfter 20 days of silence - CEO of
OL,4,CSouth East Water says 'I won't resign'
OL,6,F"I am really sorry. I have real
OL,7,Fempathy with businesses that lose
OL,8,Fmoney because of disruption - it
OL,9,Factually happens to our business quite
OL,10,Fa bit," he said.
OL,12,FHe added that the company has already
OL,13,Fcompensated businesses faster than is
OL,14,Frequired.
