OL,3,CAfter 20 days of silence - CEO of
OL,4,CSouth East Water says 'I won't resign'
OL,6,F"We're really cognisant of that," he
OL,7,Fsaid. "We have 15 days from the end of
OL,8,Fthe incident to make the compensation
OL,9,Fpayments into the accounts and we did
OL,10,Fit in one working day. So we're really
OL,11,Fconscious of that liquidity issue
OL,12,Fcustomers are facing."
OL,14,FAccording to Hinton, household
OL,15,Fcustomers will receive their
OL,16,Fcompensation by Friday (December 19th)
OL,17,Fwhich will be worth 'approximately two
OL,18,Fyears worth of water bills' for the
OL,19,Fworst affected.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G8/15
