OL,3,CAfter 20 days of silence - CEO of
OL,4,CSouth East Water says 'I won't resign'
OL,6,F"If you're a small business you're
OL,7,Flikely to get three or four multiples
OL,8,Fof your annual bill," he said. South
OL,9,FEast Water is also setting up a fund
OL,10,Fto help businesses which were impacted.
OL,12,FAs the water outage moved beyond the
OL,13,Ffirst day, South East Water faced
OL,14,Fsignificant criticism for its reaction
OL,15,Fto the crisis and the way it
OL,16,Fdistributed bottled water. Mike
OL,17,FMartin, the local MP for Tunbridge
OL,18,FWells, called the company's response a
OL,19,F'total shambles'.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G9/15
