OL,3,CAfter 20 days of silence - CEO of
OL,4,CSouth East Water says 'I won't resign'
OL,6,FIn hindsight, Hinton said, "We would
OL,7,Fselect a different site. That would be
OL,8,Fa definite learning point. and maybe
OL,9,Fwe might have been less optimistic
OL,10,Fabout the resolution, but that is a
OL,11,Fhalf a day difference. "
OL,13,FHe added: "We've had some really good
OL,14,Fcompliments from customers about their
OL,15,Fexperience at the bottled water sites."
