OL,3,CAfter 20 days of silence - CEO of
OL,4,CSouth East Water says 'I won't resign'
OL,6,FLooking ahead, Mr Hinton says the
OL,7,Fcompany is investing heavily in
OL,8,Fimproving its infrastructure. The
OL,9,Ftreatment works at Pembury was first
OL,10,Fbuilt in the 1880s. "Clearly we
OL,11,Fupgrade it as we go along," he said.
OL,13,F"In the last few years we've spent #6
OL,14,Fmillion in this site. And we've got #8
OL,15,Fmillion planned in the next two or
OL,16,Fthree years. We regularly maintain it
OL,17,Fand then we come to a big
OL,18,Frefurbishment which we're doing in
OL,19,F2028."
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}  G11/15
