OL,4,CSouth East Water says 'I won't resign'
OL,6,FHowever, he criticised the lack of
OL,7,Ffunding for revamping the country's
OL,8,Faging water infrastructure.
OL,10,F"We've put in business plans with #300
OL,11,Fmillion of extra resilience," he said.
OL,12,F"We've been fighting with the
OL,13,Fregulatory system to get that funded."
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}  G12/15
