OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax     F419A1766239620
OL,3,CAfter 20 days of silence - CEO of
OL,4,CSouth East Water says 'I won't resign'
OL,6,F"We didn't get enough by the
OL,7,Fregulatory system so we appealed to
OL,8,Fthe CMA (Competition and Markets
OL,9,FAuthority) to get that money. It's the
OL,10,Ffirst time a company has appealed to
OL,11,Fthe CMA to get that money. We need the
OL,12,Finfrastructure to actually properly
OL,13,Fimprove the resilience."
OL,15,FFor now, Mr Hinton is confident this
OL,16,Fis the end of the disruption which has
OL,17,Fplagued Tunbridge Wells.
