OL,3,CAfter 20 days of silence - CEO of
OL,4,CSouth East Water says 'I won't resign'
OL,6,F"This works in particular has got a
OL,7,Fnew coagulant - it's got options, and
OL,8,Fwe've got an extra filtration step on
OL,9,Fthe end - so this is one of the
OL,10,Fsecurer sites in our portfolio," he
OL,11,Fsaid.
OL,13,FBut he suggested nothing is certain -
OL,14,Fand did not rule out more issues in
OL,15,Fthe future.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}  G14/15
