OL,3,CAfter 20 days of silence - CEO of
OL,4,CSouth East Water says 'I won't resign'
OL,6,F"You can never say never. The thing
OL,7,Fabout water assets is they are very
OL,8,Fopen to the environment. They work
OL,9,Fintrinsically with the environment -
OL,10,Fso the environment tends to throw
OL,11,Fthings at you," he said.
OL,13,F"So I can never give a cast-iron
OL,14,Fguarantee, but nobody who runs a water
OL,15,Fcompany in the world could. But I am
OL,16,Freally confident that we've got some
OL,17,Freal resilience at the (Tunbridge
OL,18,FWells) site now."
